          'Understand store traffic volume, referral sources, and estimated daily earnings. Activate a TrendTrack Promo Code today to save on premium plans.',
        icon: 'tabler:arrows-right-left',
      },
      {
        title: 'Flexible & Trusted Intelligence',
        description:
          'A consolidated platform replaces multiple disjointed spying subscriptions. Apply your verified TrendTrack Promo Code to minimize your tool stack expenses.',
        icon: 'tabler:bulb',
      },
    ]}
  />

