      },
      {
        title: 'How do I use a TrendTrack Promo Code?',
        description:
          'To apply your TrendTrack Promo Code, pick a subscription plan on the official website, proceed to the checkout screen, and type your coupon code into the "Discount code" box. The total amount will be discounted by 20% immediately.',
      },
      {
